DATA REUSE NOTICE

Court rulings ingested by sententim are sourced from public-domain registries:

  · Sąd Najwyższy judgments via SAOS (System Analizy Orzeczeń Sądowych,
    CeON ICM University of Warsaw). Polish judicial decisions are excluded
    from copyright protection under art. 4 of the Polish Act on Copyright
    and Related Rights (ustawa o prawie autorskim i prawach pokrewnych).

  · CJEU judgments via CELLAR (Publications Office of the European Union),
    reusable under Commission Decision 2011/833/EU.

Two-sentence summaries are derived works generated by a large language model
under the supervision of the maintainers; they are released under CC-BY 4.0.
